{"id":28747,"date":"2024-02-03T05:58:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-03T00:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=28747"},"modified":"2022-08-30T15:03:53","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T09:33:53","slug":"contemporary-bedroom-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/contemporary-bedroom-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Smart Contemporary Bedroom Designs That Are Functional And Beautiful"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Turn your bedroom into a luxurious paradise with these contemporary bedroom design ideas<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Contemporary bedroom design is recently gaining popularity because of its uber cool look, universal appeal and fuss-free style. This design is easy to embrace and amalgamate with any other modern style to make your home a comforting haven. The contemporary bedroom design is innovative, functional and space-saving as well. So if you love a simple and elegant design with clean lines, dramatic flair and a touch of glamour, these chic contemporary bedroom interior design ideas will blow your mind. So what are you waiting for? Get ready to give your bedroom a 5-star makeover with these contemporary bedroom design trends.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tips and tricks to ace the contemporary bedroom design:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Stick to minimal aesthetics and clutter-free space<\/li><li>Opt for some fun and functional furniture&nbsp;<\/li><li>Choose clean lines and smooth surfaces<\/li><li>Make abundant use of natural shades with an occasional bold accent<\/li><li>Emphasise simplicity with minimal ornamentation<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s find out how to incorporate these simple tips and transform your bedroom into a sleek retreat for relaxation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Contemporary Bedroom With A Bottle Green Accent Wall And Matching Elements<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pastel hues are the signature feature of contemporary design aesthetics, but if you love a pop of vibrance in your bedroom, you have the complete freedom to experiment. The secret is to strike the perfect balance. In this contemporary bedroom design, we have used a soothing bottle green colour to accentuate the wall but maintained straight clean lines to keep the authenticity of the contemporary theme intact. The grey headboard, white panelling on the walls and white comforter and cushion covers offset the vibrance of green and lend a serene vibe. Opt for simple decor elements like some wall paintings and rattan lampshades to stitch the look together. The side cabinets with white and green laminates act as a statement piece while offering space to organise your essentials in a clutter-free manner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180317\/contemporary-bedroom-with-green-accent-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bedroom with green accent wall and matching elements brings a tropical vibe\" class=\"wp-image-28753\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180317\/contemporary-bedroom-with-green-accent-wall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180317\/contemporary-bedroom-with-green-accent-wall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180317\/contemporary-bedroom-with-green-accent-wall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180317\/contemporary-bedroom-with-green-accent-wall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bring in a tropical vibe to your contemporary bedroom design with green patterned wallpaper<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Chic Contemporary Bedroom Design With Pastel Hues And Wooden Accents<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wood brings in a lot of warmth to any interior space. Embrace the beauty of wood by introducing it in the form of panelling on an accent wall in your bedroom. We have kept a subtle pastel hue to match the design theme. Opt for simple yet luxury contemporary bedroom furniture like a comfortable bed and some side tables to keep the essence of the design aesthetics intact. Go for simple accents like pendant lights, floor to ceiling curtains and a modern painting to elevate your bedroom&#8217;s look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180311\/contemporary-bedroom-interior-design-with-pastel-hues-and-wooden-accents.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bedroom interior design with pastel hues and wooden accent lends warmth to the space\" class=\"wp-image-28752\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180311\/contemporary-bedroom-interior-design-with-pastel-hues-and-wooden-accents.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180311\/contemporary-bedroom-interior-design-with-pastel-hues-and-wooden-accents-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180311\/contemporary-bedroom-interior-design-with-pastel-hues-and-wooden-accents-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180311\/contemporary-bedroom-interior-design-with-pastel-hues-and-wooden-accents-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Lend some warmth to your modern contemporary bedroom interior design with some wooden accents<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Japanese-Inspired Contemporary Bedroom Interior Design For A Boho Vibe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Japanese design is known to be fresh, simple yet stylish and trendy. This contemporary bedroom interior design is perfect for people with a bohemian soul. The grey accent wall, rattan pendant lights, ceiling with wooden rafters and a rattan accent chair bring a soothing vibe to the entire space. The wooden bed with side tables and a cushioned bench add to the functionality and aesthetics of this contemporary Japanese-inspired bedroom while elevating your comfort quotient. You can place some potted <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/air-purifying-indoor-plants\/\">indoor plants<\/a> and a macrame wall hanging to take your boho design game a notch higher.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180323\/japanese-inspired-contemporary-bedroom-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"A contemporary bedroom in Japanese style is a perfect contemporary bedroom idea for people with a bohemian soul\" class=\"wp-image-28754\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180323\/japanese-inspired-contemporary-bedroom-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180323\/japanese-inspired-contemporary-bedroom-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180323\/japanese-inspired-contemporary-bedroom-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180323\/japanese-inspired-contemporary-bedroom-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Add a breezy vibe to your home with a contemporary Japanese bedroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Contemporary Bedroom Design With A Smart Work From Home Setup<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want some contemporary trendy bedroom decor ideas? We have got you some stylish options that are sustainable as well. The natural cork wallpaper is sustainable and adds a texture to your bedroom interiors. Opt for upcycled wood to design your contemporary bedroom furniture. The rustic look of this furniture will add an edge to your modern contemporary bedroom interiors. We have also added a study setup beside the window to elevate the functionality of the space. Pair it up with some space-saving contemporary bedroom furniture like a modular wardrobe with organisers and pull-out units or a side table with storage for a smart clutter-free lifestyle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180305\/contemporary-bedroom-design-with-a-smart-work-from-home-setup.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bedroom design with desk and natural cork wallpaper is sustainable and adds a texture\" class=\"wp-image-28751\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180305\/contemporary-bedroom-design-with-a-smart-work-from-home-setup.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180305\/contemporary-bedroom-design-with-a-smart-work-from-home-setup-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180305\/contemporary-bedroom-design-with-a-smart-work-from-home-setup-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180305\/contemporary-bedroom-design-with-a-smart-work-from-home-setup-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A multi-functional bedroom designed with contemporary design sensibilities<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An All-White Attic Bedroom With Clean Lines And Fuss-Free Design Sensibilities<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make use of your attic space by turning it into a cosy, dreamy bedroom. This all-white scheme makes your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/attic-bedroom-designs\/\">attic bedroom<\/a> look vibrant and matches the contemporary theme perfectly. The large window, simple aesthetics, a master bed adorned with white bedding and blue cushions look light to the eye and create a serene vibe. The side storage by the bed helps in arranging your books and other belongings in a clutter-free manner. You can use some wall paintings or photographs and a tall indoor plant to accentuate the beauty of this modern contemporary bedroom. You can also consider this design if you\u2019re looking for some sleek contemporary kids bedroom design ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180252\/attic-modern-contemporary-bedroom-in-all-white.jpg\" alt=\"Attic modern contemporary bedroom in all-white with large window and indoor plant accentuate the beauty of space\" class=\"wp-image-28749\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180252\/attic-modern-contemporary-bedroom-in-all-white.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180252\/attic-modern-contemporary-bedroom-in-all-white-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180252\/attic-modern-contemporary-bedroom-in-all-white-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180252\/attic-modern-contemporary-bedroom-in-all-white-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bring in a sense of serenity to your contemporary bedroom design with an all-white colour scheme<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Some Luxury Contemporary Bedroom Furniture That Is Stylish And Extremely Desirable<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Furniture plays an important role in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interiors<\/a>. They add functionality to your room and elevate the look of the space as well. With apartments getting smaller, smart and space-saving furniture is the need of the hour. So we have added some unique pieces of furniture that add to the functionality of the space while lending a luxurious vibe. The master bed with an upholstered headboard in white is perfect for snuggling on after a long day of work. We have added a floor to ceiling wardrobe with handleless doors to give a clean look and finish. The side tables on either side of the bed come with drawers and open shelves for you to keep your books and other knick-knacks. The navy blue accent wall cuts the monotony of muted colours and brings focus to the beautiful decor elements like the wall paints and pendant lights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180330\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-that-is-stylish.jpg\" alt=\"Modern contemporary master bedroom with unique pieces of furniture adds to the functionality of the space\" class=\"wp-image-28755\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180330\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-that-is-stylish.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180330\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-that-is-stylish-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180330\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-that-is-stylish-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/02180330\/luxury-contemporary-bedroom-furniture-that-is-stylish-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Beautify your modern contemporary master bedroom with some smart modular furniture and simple decor elements<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n